{"tid":2083702,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android 12抄襲返iOS！Google欲全面拋棄對32位元的支援","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T09:49:51.000Z","uid":109923,"like":12,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc5af3b291f86853d6ff7dacaf900550c064363","tid":2083702,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"因為32位元的固有限制，不少主流系統已經切換到64位元環境，譬如iOS 11、macOS Catalina等，Windows 10也自v2004版本開始停止向OEM分發32位元系統。下面該Android了。據開發者爆料Android S（按照字母排序，對應Android 12系統）的x86_64模擬器已經停止對32位元的支援，此乃破天荒的頭一次。<br />\n<br />\n實際上Google Play商店自2019年8月1日開始強制要求開發者切換到64位元程式，也許就是在為Android S系統做準備。開發者認為向64位元的遷移有助於減少RAM佔用、減少空間佔用以及提高底層安全。另外ARM全新的Cortex A65架構已經是純64位元CPU，刪除了32位元指令集。<br />\n<br />\n根據此前iOS 11上的經驗，明年的Android S（Android 12）上，那些老舊的32位元程式很可能無法直接執行。<br />\n<br />\n早在 iOS 10.3 時代，Apple 對所有執行的 32-bit Apps 顯示「未來 iOS 不再支援」的宣言，讓用戶有心理準備 Apple 隨時停止 32-bit Apps 支援。最終在iOS 11 Developer Beta 1 中全面封鎖 32-bit Apps，不論在 App Store 未能以 Search 功能找出這些 Apps，即使點這些 32-bit Apps 的連結也會顯示 iOS 11 不能執行這些 Apps。"},{"pid":"2b84f218379b1e21a0da37ab84eef1bf18fdf9a2","tid":2083702,"uid":63885,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0L8EhQr.jpg&amp;h=2509aa37&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"79754af27a6354ac89ce92d246cad07c3e5dddee","tid":2083702,"uid":114487,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEpj5kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEpj5kb.jpg&h=d66f7ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2KDBrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2KDBrX.jpg&h=a5c2a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4w0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4w0k.jpg&h=82cb5faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n決定